               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1" to="28v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3582Prayer">Ṣalot wa-ʾastabqʷǝʿot ḫaba ʾǝgzǝʾǝtǝna Māryām za-yǝtnabbab
          ba-lelit</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ዝንቱ፡ ጸሎት፡ ወስእለት፡ ወአስተብቍዖት፡ ኃበ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ወመድኃኒትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ዘይትነበብ፡ በሌሊት።
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ይጸግወነ፡ ለኵልነ፡ ሣህሎ፡ ወምሕረቶ፡ ወይክፍለነ፡ መ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ግሥቶ፡ አመ፡ ዳግም፡ ምጽአቱ፡ ያቁመነ፡ ቅድሜሁ፡ አመ፡ ያቀውም፡ 
                        ዓባግዐ፡ በየማኑ፡ ወአጣሌ፡ በፀጋሙ። ያቁመነ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ወያስተሳትፈነ፡ እመክ<supplied reason="omitted">ፈ</supplied>ልቶሙ፡ በሰላም፡ ወበጽድቅ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ወአምላክነ፡ 
                        ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምይእዜ፡ ወእስከ፡ ለዓ<supplied reason="omitted">ለ</supplied>መ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                     </explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="28v" to="32v"/>
                     <title type="complete">Prayer to Our Lord Jesus Christ</title>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        መሀረነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ በስእለታ፡ ለወላዲትከ። ኦወሀቤ፡ ምሕረት፡ እስመ፡ ኃልቀ፡ መዋዕሊነ፡ ወኃለፈ፡ ዓመታቲነ።፡ ወአልብነ፡ ተስፋ፡ ካልእ፡ መዋዕል።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>Presumably copied from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet15#p1_i19"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BAVet15#p1_i19</span></ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="33r" to="40v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4707Salot#Sunday">
                        
                           <sic>ወዳሴ፡</sic>
                         በሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን።</title>
                     <note>Presumably copied from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet15#p1_i10.1"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BAVet15#p1_i10.1</span></ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="41" to="69v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2362Songof">Song of Songs</title>
                     <note>The text is followed by a short doxology and an <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6946InvocationMary">invocation of Mary</ref>:
                     <q xml:lang="gez">ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። ለዓለም። ወለዓለመ፡ ዓለም። ሰአሊ፡ ለነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ማርያም፡ ምሕረተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልድኪ፡ የሃውጸነ፡ እምአርያም። 
                     ኦአምላከ፡ ሰሎሞን፡ ወዳዊት፡ አድኅነነ፡ እምዕለት፡ እኪት፡ ወባልሀነ፡ እምኵሉ፡ መንሱት።</q>.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="70r" to="71v"/>
                     <title type="complete">Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps71"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps71</span></ref> 1-10</title>
                  </msItem>
